summary: This mod simply adds a Female Giant NPC.  Chose woodelf race but with the \"ice\" eyes to somewhat resemble the vanilla giants.
descriptionHtml:
This mod simply adds a Female Giant NPC named Tess.  Chose woodelf race but with the \"ice\" eyes to somewhat resemble the vanilla giants.

Her location is the miniature island with the fisherman in the Ilinalta Lake.  West of Riverwood.  Can\'t miss her, she\'s 20 feet tall.
author: Buffscale McThundertail
